%I A395305 #12 May 02 2026 11:05:02
%S A395305 1,0,0,1,0,1,0,3,2,16,21,116
%N A395305 Number of triangle-patch-irreducible dissections of an equilateral triangle into n equilateral triangles, up to symmetry.
%C A395305 A dissection is triangle-patch-irreducible if it contains no proper equilateral-triangle patch tiled by at least two of its tiles.
%C A395305 This is not restricted to separated dissections.
%H A395305 Aleš Drápal and Carlo Hämäläinen, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/0910.5199">An enumeration of equilateral triangle dissections</a>, arXiv:0910.5199 [math.CO], 2010.
%Y A395305 Cf. A167123, A299705, A221841, A221842.
%K A395305 nonn,more,new
%O A395305 1,8
%A A395305 _Vicente Valle_, Apr 19 2026
